enb_long_title: Eleventh session of the Conference of the Parties to the Climate Change Convention and first meeting of the Parties to the Kyoto Protocol
sentences: The COP/MOP considered its provisional agenda for the meeting on 28 November.
While the agenda was generally agreeable, the EU objected to the inclusion of the item on Protocol Article 2.3 (response measures) in the agenda on the grounds that it was being addressed elsewhere.
Saudi Arabia objected to its removal.
The agenda was adopted as presented, with this item held in abeyance (FCCC/KP/CMP/2005/1/Add.1).
